data-triple-N3.o: "Queens Park Rangers Football Club (usually referred to as QPR) is an English professional football club, based in White City, London. As the 201011 Football League Championship champions, they now play in the top tier of English football, the Premier League, for the first time in 15 years. Other honours include winning the League Cup in 1967, being runners-up in the old First Division in 197576 and reaching the final of the FA Cup in 1982."@en
